1 University Drive&nbsp;<br />
Aliso Viejo, CA 92656</p>

<p>(949) 480-4342 | Fax: (949) 480-4151 |&nbsp;<a href="mailto:financialaid@soka.edu" target="_blank">financialaid@soka.edu</a></p>

<h3>Office Hours</h3>

<p>We are open from 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m., Monday through Friday. Our offices are located on the second floor of Founders Hall. To schedule an appointment, please email&nbsp;<a href="mailto:financialaid@soka.edu" target="_blank">financialaid@soka.edu</a>.&nbsp;</p>

      
  
